<section class="scene" id="scene-3" aria-labelledby="work-h">
  <div class="scene-label">Featured work</div>
  <h2 class="scene-title" id="work-h">Outcomes,<br><em>not outputs.</em></h2>
  <div class="work-scroll-track" id="work-track" role="list">
    <article class="case-card-imm" role="listitem" aria-labelledby="c1">
      <div class="case-tag-imm">Shopify · Brand Identity</div>
      <div class="case-brand-imm" id="c1">Solera</div>
      <p class="case-desc-imm">Entering a saturated skincare market with no digital presence. Needed a brand and store capable of converting cold traffic from day one.</p>
      <div class="case-metrics-imm">
        <div class="case-metric-row"><span class="case-metric-val">+28%</span><span class="case-metric-lbl">CVR vs<br>industry avg</span></div>
        <div class="case-metric-row"><span class="case-metric-val">6 days</span><span class="case-metric-lbl">Launch<br>timeline</span></div>
        <div class="case-metric-row"><span class="case-metric-val">+19%</span><span class="case-metric-lbl">AOV<br>lift</span></div>
      </div>
    </article>
    <article class="case-card-imm" role="listitem" aria-labelledby="c2">
      <div class="case-tag-imm">WooCommerce · Growth Systems</div>
      <div class="case-brand-imm" id="c2">Varka</div>
      <p class="case-desc-imm">Existing store suffering from slow load times, poor mobile UX, and no post-purchase retention system. Rebuilt from the ground up.</p>
      <div class="case-metrics-imm">
        <div class="case-metric-row"><span class="case-metric-val">-42%</span><span class="case-metric-lbl">Page load<br>time</span></div>
        <div class="case-metric-row"><span class="case-metric-val">+22%</span><span class="case-metric-lbl">Repeat purchase<br>rate</span></div>
        <div class="case-metric-row"><span class="case-metric-val">+14%</span><span class="case-metric-lbl">AOV</span></div>
      </div>
    </article>
    <article class="case-card-imm" role="listitem" aria-labelledby="c3">
      <div class="case-tag-imm">Shopify · Brand · CRO</div>
      <div class="case-brand-imm" id="c3">Dune</div>
      <p class="case-desc-imm">Apparel brand pivoting from wholesale to DTC. Needed a flagship store and full brand system built for conversion from day one.</p>
      <div class="case-metrics-imm">
        <div class="case-metric-row"><span class="case-metric-val">+34%</span><span class="case-metric-lbl">CVR<br>improvement</span></div>
        <div class="case-metric-row"><span class="case-metric-val">7 days</span><span class="case-metric-lbl">Full<br>launch</span></div>
        <div class="case-metric-row"><span class="case-metric-val">3.8x</span><span class="case-metric-lbl">ROAS<br>month 1</span></div>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
  <p class="drag-hint">Drag to explore</p>
</section>
